name: Deluxe Dry Sack
description: Waterproof Dry Sack with shoulder strap. Water protection for the things that should always be with you while you are fishing, kayaking, canoeing, hiking, rafting, boating, snowboard going to a water park or taking a long trip to the mountains, forest or to the national park, spending time near a pool or at the beach, going to the ocean, sea, river, lake. Duluxe Dry Sack is made of hardwearing reinforced PVC Tarpaulin 500 den thick, waterproof and safe locked. It has a one-shoulder strong belt that is easy to fasten. After use, the bag needs very little storing space in your luggage or on a shelf.
